  Stable on ppc.

  14 Mar 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> mono-1.0.4.ebuild:
  Mark a 1.0.4 mono stable too.

  14 Mar 2005; Peter Johanson <latexer@gentoo.org> -files/mono-1.0-segv.diff,
  -mono-0.28.ebuild, -mono-1.0.2-r1.ebuild, -mono-1.0.2.ebuild,
